<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Fixed Header with Dropdown</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>

  <header class="header">
    <h1>Welcome</h1>
    <button id="menuButton" class="menu-button">Toggle Menu</button>
    <div id="dropdownMenu" class="dropdown-menu">
      <ul>
        <li><a href="#home">Home</a></li>
          <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
          <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="content">
    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Cum molestiae culpa nesciunt doloremque, provident consequuntur, quidem repellendus ipsum reiciendis doloribus dolorum, quod quis quos nostrum! Animi, eligendi mollitia. Error, consequuntur.</p>
  </div>

  <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>



* {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }
  
 
  .header {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    background-color: #333;
    color: white;
    padding: 10px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    z-index: 1000;
  }
  
  .menu-button {
    background-color: #444;
    color: white;
    border: none;
    padding: 10px;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  
  .menu-button:hover {
    background-color: #555;
  }
  
  .dropdown-menu {
    display: none;
    position: absolute;
    top: 50px; 
    right: 0;
    background-color: #444;
    padding: 10px;
    width: 150px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
   
  }
  
  .dropdown-menu ul {
    list-style: none;
  
  }
  
  .dropdown-menu li {
    padding: 8px;
    color: white;
  }

  .dropdown-menu ul li a {
    text-decoration: none;
    color: #ffffff;
  }
  
  .dropdown-menu li:hover {
    background-color: #555;
  }
  

  .content {
    margin-top: 60px; 
    padding: 20px;
    height: 2000px;
  }


3rd question
const menuButton = document.getElementById('menuButton');
const dropdownMenu = document.getElementById('dropdownMenu');


menuButton.addEventListener('click', () => {
  const isMenuVisible = dropdownMenu.style.display === 'block';
  dropdownMenu.style.display = isMenuVisible ? 'none' : 'block';
});


body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
  }
  
  .container {
    padding: 20px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 3rem);
  }
  
  p {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 3vw, 2rem); 
  }